ANGEL'S DESTINY forwardly placed inside, bid two wide into the stretch and just missed getting up for second. HALO EFFECT pressed the pace two wide for a half, gained a narrow lead, set a pressured pace past the quarter pole and weakened in deep stretch. LATE DATE was always outrun. BUSYBEING FABULOUS set the early pace while getting out, gave up the lead before a half, had speed into the stretch, drifted wide and sopped.
